845
00:43:14,880 --> 00:43:16,380
[SPEAKER_01] zašto nama mladi izlaze iz Hrvatske.

846
00:43:16,380 --> 00:43:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je uzrok

847
00:43:18,000 --> 00:43:19,559
[SPEAKER_01] zašto je 600 tisuća ljudi

848
00:43:19,559 --> 00:43:20,400
[SPEAKER_01] pobjeglo iz Hrvatske.

849
00:43:20,400 --> 00:43:21,599
[SPEAKER_01] I onda te, te

850
00:43:21,599 --> 00:43:22,920
[SPEAKER_01] megalomanske,

851
00:43:22,920 --> 00:43:23,940
[SPEAKER_01] bjedne laži

852
00:43:23,940 --> 00:43:25,099
[SPEAKER_01] o tim njegovim uspjesima,

853
00:43:25,099 --> 00:43:26,159
[SPEAKER_01] Plenkovića, Milanovića,

854
00:43:26,159 --> 00:43:26,539
[SPEAKER_01] tako dalje,

855
00:43:26,539 --> 00:43:27,400
[SPEAKER_01] Schengen, Euro.

856
00:43:27,460 --> 00:43:28,480
[SPEAKER_01] Znate koji još jedan u nizu

857
00:43:28,480 --> 00:43:30,239
[SPEAKER_01] tih onako grotesnih primjera.

858
00:43:30,239 --> 00:43:31,820
[SPEAKER_01] Zakon o hrvatskom jeziku.

859
00:43:31,820 --> 00:43:32,219
[SPEAKER_01] Pazite,

860
00:43:32,219 --> 00:43:34,420
[SPEAKER_01] toliko su se hvalili

861
00:43:34,420 --> 00:43:35,619
[SPEAKER_01] i slavili taj,

862
00:43:35,619 --> 00:43:36,420
[SPEAKER_01] čak su i ploču,

863
00:43:36,420 --> 00:43:36,699
[SPEAKER_01] ja mislim,

864
00:43:36,699 --> 00:43:37,860
[SPEAKER_01] stavili u matice Hrvatskoj.

865
00:43:37,860 --> 00:43:39,420
[SPEAKER_01] Za veliko postignuća

866
00:43:39,420 --> 00:43:40,639
[SPEAKER_01] oni su donijeli zakon

867
00:43:40,639 --> 00:43:41,559
[SPEAKER_01] o hrvatskom jeziku.

868
00:43:41,559 --> 00:43:42,699
[SPEAKER_01] Ja neki dan dolazim

869
00:43:42,699 --> 00:43:43,500
[SPEAKER_01] u Slasečarnicu

870
00:43:43,500 --> 00:43:44,400
[SPEAKER_01] u centru Zagreba

871
00:43:44,400 --> 00:43:45,260
[SPEAKER_01] ne mogu naručiti kavu

872
00:43:45,260 --> 00:43:46,440
[SPEAKER_01] jer žena ne govori

873
00:43:46,440 --> 00:43:46,980
[SPEAKER_01] hrvatske,

874
00:43:46,980 --> 00:43:47,699
[SPEAKER_01] nego govori engleske.

875
00:43:47,699 --> 00:43:49,760
[SPEAKER_01] Žena nije kriva.

876
00:43:49,840 --> 00:43:50,719
[SPEAKER_01] Meni je žao tih ljudi.

877
00:43:50,719 --> 00:43:51,559
[SPEAKER_01] Oni su dovedeni ovdje

878
00:43:51,559 --> 00:43:52,739
[SPEAKER_01] koliko treće razredno roblje.

879
00:43:52,739 --> 00:43:54,440
[SPEAKER_01] To je sramota i za Hrvatsku.

880
00:43:54,440 --> 00:43:55,659
[SPEAKER_01] Ali opet nije naša sramota,

881
00:43:55,659 --> 00:43:56,920
[SPEAKER_01] nego onih koji vode u državu.

882
00:43:56,920 --> 00:43:58,079
[SPEAKER_01] Žena dođe,

883
00:43:58,079 --> 00:43:58,500
[SPEAKER_01] kumica,

884
00:43:58,500 --> 00:43:59,480
[SPEAKER_01] gospodža,

885
00:43:59,480 --> 00:43:59,940
[SPEAKER_01] baka,

886
00:43:59,940 --> 00:44:00,719
[SPEAKER_01] u konzum.

887
00:44:00,719 --> 00:44:01,860
[SPEAKER_01] Ne može naručiti meso,

888
00:44:01,860 --> 00:44:02,739
[SPEAKER_01] kupiti meso

889
00:44:02,739 --> 00:44:04,139
[SPEAKER_01] jer je čovjek ne razumije.

890
00:44:04,139 --> 00:44:05,320
[SPEAKER_01] Gdje je tu zakon

891
00:44:05,320 --> 00:44:06,079
[SPEAKER_01] o hrvatskom jeziku?

892
00:44:06,079 --> 00:44:06,760
[SPEAKER_01] Pazite,

893
00:44:06,760 --> 00:44:07,599
[SPEAKER_01] moj otac je bio

894
00:44:07,599 --> 00:44:09,619
[SPEAKER_01] kao mlad čovjek

895
00:44:09,619 --> 00:44:11,139
[SPEAKER_01] suočen s takvom realnošću.

896
00:44:11,139 --> 00:44:12,440
[SPEAKER_01] On je iselio u Njemačku,

897
00:44:19,840 --> 00:44:21,559
[SPEAKER_01] javnoj komunikaciji.

898
00:44:21,559 --> 00:44:23,940
[SPEAKER_01] Ali raditi u javnom prostoru,

899
00:44:23,940 --> 00:44:24,800
[SPEAKER_01] a ne znati jezik.

900
00:44:24,800 --> 00:44:25,880
[SPEAKER_01] Pa pazite,

901
00:44:25,880 --> 00:44:26,760
[SPEAKER_01] imate rigorozne,

902
00:44:26,760 --> 00:44:28,579
[SPEAKER_01] opet ćemo kod državnog inspektorata

903
00:44:28,579 --> 00:44:29,039
[SPEAKER_01] zamršiti,

904
00:44:29,039 --> 00:44:30,699
[SPEAKER_01] rigorozne mjere

905
00:44:30,699 --> 00:44:32,139
[SPEAKER_01] da moraju ljudi prolaziti,

906
00:44:32,139 --> 00:44:33,019
[SPEAKER_01] ne znam,

907
00:44:33,019 --> 00:44:34,099
[SPEAKER_01] tečajeve,

908
00:44:34,099 --> 00:44:35,079
[SPEAKER_01] instrukcije.

909
00:44:35,079 --> 00:44:36,179
[SPEAKER_01] Pa na kojem jeziku

910
00:44:36,179 --> 00:44:37,420
[SPEAKER_01] polažu ti radnici sve?

911
00:44:37,420 --> 00:44:38,800
[SPEAKER_01] Razumijete?

912
00:44:38,800 --> 00:44:39,320
[SPEAKER_00] Dobro što?

913
00:44:39,320 --> 00:44:40,219
[SPEAKER_00] To je njihov veliki upis.

914
00:44:40,219 --> 00:44:41,500
[SPEAKER_00] Dobro tebi ste već par put

915
00:44:41,500 --> 00:44:42,739
[SPEAKER_01] zakon na hrvatskom jeziku.

916
00:44:42,739 --> 00:44:43,440
[SPEAKER_00] Piknuli,

917
00:44:43,440 --> 00:44:44,000
[SPEAKER_00] dakle,

918
00:44:44,000 --> 00:44:45,059
[SPEAKER_00] te strane radnike,

919
00:44:45,059 --> 00:44:46,500
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno pred našim očima

920
00:44:46,500 --> 00:44:47,739
[SPEAKER_00] izmjenu stanovništva.

921
00:44:47,739 --> 00:44:48,940
[SPEAKER_00] Možemo to tako reći.

922
00:44:48,940 --> 00:44:49,619
[SPEAKER_01] I pazite,

923
00:44:49,619 --> 00:44:51,260
[SPEAKER_01] onda gospođa iz Zdromina

924
00:44:51,260 --> 00:44:52,099
[SPEAKER_01] govori o tome

925
00:44:52,099 --> 00:44:53,500
[SPEAKER_01] kako je to zamjena stanovništva,

926
00:44:53,500 --> 00:44:54,559
[SPEAKER_01] a pokroviteljom je

927
00:44:54,559 --> 00:44:55,360
[SPEAKER_01] Pavel Vujnovac

928
00:44:55,360 --> 00:44:56,159
[SPEAKER_01] i Mario Radić

929
00:44:56,159 --> 00:44:57,559
[SPEAKER_01] koji vrše tu zamjenu

930
00:44:57,559 --> 00:44:58,199
[SPEAKER_01] u stanovništva.

931
00:44:58,199 --> 00:44:59,480
[SPEAKER_01] Svijete vi taj paradoks?

932
00:44:59,480 --> 00:45:00,179
[SPEAKER_00] Da, kako, kako.

933
00:45:00,179 --> 00:45:00,719
[SPEAKER_00] Da, to malo.

934
00:45:00,719 --> 00:45:01,840
[SPEAKER_01] Pa koje daje veći uvoznik

935
00:45:01,840 --> 00:45:02,860
[SPEAKER_01] poče povrće u Hrvatskoj?

936
00:45:02,860 --> 00:45:03,579
[SPEAKER_01] Pavel Vujnovac.

937
00:45:03,579 --> 00:45:05,119
[SPEAKER_01] Koje stvorio Pavla Vujnovca?

938
00:45:05,119 --> 00:45:06,159
[SPEAKER_01] Stvorio ga Milanović

939
00:45:06,159 --> 00:45:08,500
[SPEAKER_01] zajedno sa Ivanom Vrdoljakom

940
00:45:08,500 --> 00:45:09,239
[SPEAKER_01] koji mu je tada bio

941
00:45:09,239 --> 00:45:10,340
[SPEAKER_01] ministar energetike.

942
00:45:10,340 --> 00:45:11,719
[SPEAKER_01] Koje od Pavla Vujnovca

943
00:45:11,719 --> 00:45:13,260
[SPEAKER_01] učinio još veće gigantat?

944
00:45:13,260 --> 00:45:14,800
[SPEAKER_01] Andrej Plenković.

945
00:45:14,800 --> 00:45:17,780
[SPEAKER_01] Taj čovjek ima pod kontrolom

946
00:45:17,780 --> 00:45:20,280
[SPEAKER_01] 20% BDP-a.

947
00:45:20,280 --> 00:45:21,920
[SPEAKER_01] Vi na godišnjoj razine

948
00:45:21,920 --> 00:45:22,800
[SPEAKER_01] nemate pet člana

949
00:45:22,800 --> 00:45:23,519
[SPEAKER_01] kao tom čovjeku.

950
00:45:23,519 --> 00:45:24,219
[SPEAKER_01] To normalno.

951
00:45:24,219 --> 00:45:25,880
[SPEAKER_01] Nitko se ne buni.

952
00:45:25,880 --> 00:45:27,500
[SPEAKER_01] Kao što se kod Mikulića

953
00:45:27,500 --> 00:45:28,199
[SPEAKER_01] niko nije bunio.

954
00:45:28,199 --> 00:45:29,440
[SPEAKER_01] Jer su svi na neki način

955
00:45:29,440 --> 00:45:30,659
[SPEAKER_01] ugrađeni.

956
00:45:30,659 --> 00:45:32,260
[SPEAKER_01] I zbog nekog svog razloga

957
00:45:32,260 --> 00:45:33,760
[SPEAKER_01] neće to dovoditi u pitanju.

958
00:45:34,440 --> 00:45:35,500
[SPEAKER_01] Pa konzum je njegov.

959
00:45:35,500 --> 00:45:37,320
[SPEAKER_01] Rastara stranih radnika

960
00:45:37,320 --> 00:45:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] koliko hoćete.

961
00:45:38,000 --> 00:45:38,599
[SPEAKER_01] Zašto?

962
00:45:38,599 --> 00:45:40,480
[SPEAKER_01] Pa je li može zaposlenica

963
00:45:40,480 --> 00:45:41,800
[SPEAKER_01] u konzumu preživiti

964
00:45:41,800 --> 00:45:43,280
[SPEAKER_01] sa 850 eura ili 900?

965
00:45:43,280 --> 00:45:43,980
[SPEAKER_01] Ne može.

966
00:45:43,980 --> 00:45:45,960
[SPEAKER_01] Pa gdje su ti novci?

967
00:45:45,960 --> 00:45:47,940
[SPEAKER_01] Pola milijuna

968
00:45:47,940 --> 00:45:50,860
[SPEAKER_01] tešku ogrlicu je švercao

969
00:45:50,860 --> 00:45:51,559
[SPEAKER_01] preko granice

970
00:45:51,559 --> 00:45:53,679
[SPEAKER_01] ali se nema za plaću radnicima.

971
00:45:53,679 --> 00:45:56,139
[SPEAKER_01] Ali ću uzeti strane radnike

972
00:45:56,139 --> 00:45:57,760
[SPEAKER_01] jer ih može mizorno platiti

973
00:45:57,760 --> 00:45:58,739
[SPEAKER_01] i možeš dobiti dodatne

974
00:45:58,739 --> 00:46:00,199
[SPEAKER_01] novce iz fondova

975
00:46:00,199 --> 00:46:01,340
[SPEAKER_01] kako je to već regulirano.

976
00:46:01,340 --> 00:46:02,880
[SPEAKER_01] Je li to domoljublje?

977
00:46:03,719 --> 00:46:05,400
[SPEAKER_01] I onda njegovi podanici

978
00:46:05,400 --> 00:46:07,360
[SPEAKER_01] vrište u medijskoj sceni

979
00:46:07,360 --> 00:46:08,920
[SPEAKER_01] o zamjenistrano nište.

980
00:46:08,920 --> 00:46:10,500
[SPEAKER_01] A sjede u tom brodu.

981
00:46:10,500 --> 00:46:12,099
[SPEAKER_01] Jer razumijete taj paradoks?

982
00:46:12,099 --> 00:46:13,619
[SPEAKER_01] To je ta

983
00:46:13,619 --> 00:46:16,179
[SPEAKER_01] institucionalizirana laž.

984
00:46:16,179 --> 00:46:17,340
[SPEAKER_01] Da hrvatski čovjek kaže

985
00:46:17,340 --> 00:46:17,619
[SPEAKER_01] ma

986
00:46:17,619 --> 00:46:19,440
[SPEAKER_01] više ništa ne vjeroje.

987
00:46:19,440 --> 00:46:20,980
[SPEAKER_01] Ma nije sve propalo.

988
00:46:20,980 --> 00:46:22,960
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, Hrvatska je prekrasna zemlja.

989
00:46:22,960 --> 00:46:23,599
[SPEAKER_01] Ovdje zaista

990
00:46:23,599 --> 00:46:24,260
[SPEAKER_01] mi nemamo

991
00:46:24,260 --> 00:46:25,460
[SPEAKER_01] kad ste rekli samo to

992
00:46:25,460 --> 00:46:26,300
[SPEAKER_01] da, samo to

993
00:46:26,300 --> 00:46:27,699
[SPEAKER_01] to nije velik zahvat.

994
00:46:27,699 --> 00:46:28,760
[SPEAKER_01] Treba

995
00:46:28,760 --> 00:46:29,719
[SPEAKER_01] mi smo strpljivi.

996
00:46:29,719 --> 00:46:30,980
[SPEAKER_01] Mi nećemo odustati.

997
00:46:30,980 --> 00:46:31,760
[SPEAKER_01] A ne može

998
00:46:31,760 --> 00:46:33,059
[SPEAKER_01] ne može majka odustati

999
00:46:33,059 --> 00:46:33,800
[SPEAKER_01] od svog djeteta.

1000
00:46:33,800 --> 00:46:34,920
[SPEAKER_01] Tako mi mi kao djeca

1001
00:46:34,920 --> 00:46:36,260
[SPEAKER_01] ne možemo odustati

1002
00:46:36,260 --> 00:46:37,860
[SPEAKER_01] od svoje majke domovine.

1003
00:46:37,860 --> 00:46:38,320
[SPEAKER_01] Je li tako?

1004
00:46:38,320 --> 00:46:38,900
[SPEAKER_01] Pa neće mene

1005
00:46:38,900 --> 00:46:39,539
[SPEAKER_01] obezkrabriti

1006
00:46:39,539 --> 00:46:43,539
[SPEAKER_00] 500 tisuća ih je odustalo

1007
00:46:43,539 --> 00:46:44,860
[SPEAKER_00] i otišlo od majke domovine?

1008
00:46:44,860 --> 00:46:46,139
[SPEAKER_01] Je li se tih 500 tisuća

1009
00:46:46,139 --> 00:46:46,679
[SPEAKER_01] može vratiti?

1010
00:46:46,679 --> 00:46:49,960
[SPEAKER_01] Vedajte, ništa nije

1011
00:46:49,960 --> 00:46:50,739
[SPEAKER_01] za vasta.

1012
00:46:50,739 --> 00:46:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] Je li tako?

1013
00:46:52,000 --> 00:46:53,619
[SPEAKER_01] Samo je mi jedna stalna.

1014
00:46:53,619 --> 00:46:55,760
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, nama je se boriti

1015
00:46:55,760 --> 00:46:56,960
[SPEAKER_01] za ispravne vrijednosti.

1016
00:46:56,960 --> 00:46:58,019
[SPEAKER_01] Hvala vam na pozivu.

1017
00:46:58,019 --> 00:46:59,059
[SPEAKER_01] Evo jedna prilika

1018
00:46:59,059 --> 00:47:00,260
[SPEAKER_01] opet za mene

1019
00:47:00,260 --> 00:47:01,360
[SPEAKER_01] i za odlučnost i pravednost

1020
00:47:01,360 --> 00:47:02,380
[SPEAKER_01] da ljudima kažemo

1021
00:47:02,380 --> 00:47:03,480
[SPEAKER_01] učlanite se.

1022
00:47:03,480 --> 00:47:04,360
[SPEAKER_01] Pridružite se.

1023
00:47:04,360 --> 00:47:06,400
[SPEAKER_01] Stranka što je jača

1024
00:47:06,400 --> 00:47:07,380
[SPEAKER_01] to su oni slabiji.

1025
00:47:07,380 --> 00:47:09,179
[SPEAKER_01] Mi znamo kamo idemo

1026
00:47:09,179 --> 00:47:09,940
[SPEAKER_01] i što želimo.

1027
00:47:09,940 --> 00:47:11,559
[SPEAKER_01] Mi želimo prave promjene

1028
00:47:11,559 --> 00:47:12,099
[SPEAKER_01] u Hrvatsku.

1029
00:47:12,099 --> 00:47:13,340
[SPEAKER_01] Mi se ne želimo ugraditi

1030
00:47:13,340 --> 00:47:13,800
[SPEAKER_01] u sustav.

1031
00:47:13,800 --> 00:47:15,340
[SPEAKER_01] I zato i nismo u tom sustavu.

1032
00:47:15,340 --> 00:47:16,960
[SPEAKER_01] I zato nas i žele zabraniti

1033
00:47:16,960 --> 00:47:17,880
[SPEAKER_01] i zato nas proganjaju.

1034
00:47:17,880 --> 00:47:18,719
[SPEAKER_01] Je li nam teško?

1035
00:47:18,719 --> 00:47:20,460
[SPEAKER_01] Je, ali to je nama.

1036
00:47:20,460 --> 00:47:21,980
[SPEAKER_01] To nam je zadatak,

1037
00:47:21,980 --> 00:47:22,820
[SPEAKER_01] dužnost.

1038
00:47:22,820 --> 00:47:24,460
[SPEAKER_01] Ja ću reći

1039
00:47:24,460 --> 00:47:25,440
[SPEAKER_01] jedna

1040
00:47:25,440 --> 00:47:27,320
[SPEAKER_01] lijepa objeza.

1041
00:47:27,320 --> 00:47:28,639
[SPEAKER_01] Hajde da vas pitam.

1042
00:47:28,639 --> 00:47:29,840
[SPEAKER_01] Je li vas tuže jako?

1043
00:47:29,840 --> 00:47:31,179
[SPEAKER_01] Pa naravno.

1044
00:47:31,179 --> 00:47:32,719
[SPEAKER_01] Ali pazite, to je njihovo pravo suđe.

1045
00:47:32,719 --> 00:47:33,940
[SPEAKER_01] Te tužbe.

1046
00:47:33,940 --> 00:47:35,179
[SPEAKER_01] Pa tko se više...

1047
00:47:35,179 --> 00:47:36,320
[SPEAKER_01] Tko vas je tužio?

1048
00:47:38,440 --> 00:47:40,059
[SPEAKER_01] Mrsić, Pavo Vujnovac.

1049
00:47:40,059 --> 00:47:42,679
[SPEAKER_01] Imate toga koliko hoćete.

1050
00:47:42,679 --> 00:47:44,079
[SPEAKER_01] Nisu problem tužbe.

1051
00:47:44,079 --> 00:47:46,579
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, ja iza svega što kažem stojim.

1052
00:47:46,579 --> 00:47:48,880
[SPEAKER_01] I nikada nisam iznosila stvari

1053
00:47:48,880 --> 00:47:50,360
[SPEAKER_01] koje nisu u istinu provjerene

1054
00:47:50,360 --> 00:47:51,559
[SPEAKER_01] jednom, dva put, pet put.

1055
00:47:51,559 --> 00:47:53,599
[SPEAKER_01] I ako se dogodi greška,

1056
00:47:53,599 --> 00:47:55,119
[SPEAKER_01] kaže se stop,

1057
00:47:55,119 --> 00:47:56,159
[SPEAKER_01] tu smo pogriješili.

1058
00:47:56,159 --> 00:47:58,119
[SPEAKER_01] I obrazloži se

1059
00:47:58,119 --> 00:47:59,179
